---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import NameGenerator from '../components/NameGenerator.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Baby Name Generator - Unique & Meaningful Baby Names"
  description="Instantly generate thousands of baby names. Filter by boy names, girl names, or gender-neutral options. Save your favorites and copy names easily."
  keywords="baby name generator, baby names, boy baby names, girl baby names, unisex baby names, unique baby names, baby name ideas"
>
  <div class="space-y-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Header/Intro -->
    <div class="text-center space-y-3">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-[#111111] dark:text-white leading-none">
        Baby Name Generator
      </h1>
      <p class="text-base text-[#666666] dark:text-[#888888] max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Discover the perfect name for your little one. Whether you are looking for timeless classics, modern ideas, or unique gender-neutral options, find it here.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Generator Component -->
    <NameGenerator category="baby" categoryName="Baby" />

    <!-- SEO Content Section -->
    <section class="border-t border-[#e5e7eb] dark:border-[#222222] pt-10 mt-12 space-y-6 text-[#666666] dark:text-[#888888] text-sm leading-relaxed theme-transition">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-[#111111] dark:text-white">Tips for Choosing Your Baby's Name</h2>
      <p>
        Naming a child is one of the most exciting and meaningful decisions of parenthood. Here are some strategies to help narrow down your choices:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
        <li><strong>Say it Out Loud:</strong> Test how the first name sounds alongside your last name. Listen to the rhythm, syllable count, and flow.</li>
        <li><strong>Check the Initials:</strong> Make sure the initials don't spell out anything embarrassing or unwanted.</li>
        <li><strong>Consider Nicknames:</strong> Think about what shortened versions children or friends might use as they grow up, and make sure you like them.</li>
        <li><strong>Look Up Meanings:</strong> Many parents find inspiration in names with strong definitions, such as strength, peace, joy, or nature.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
